headline: Old El Paso Brings the Heat with New Birria Taco Kit, Breakfast Taco Kit and Expanded Carb Advantage Line
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, March 25, 2025--Fire up the stove and grab your favorite taco seasoning — Old El Paso is bringing the ultimate Tex-Mex fiesta to kitchens everywhere. As the go-to brand for easy, delicious, and fun-filled taco nights, Old El Paso is making it even simpler to enjoy big and bold flavors from breakfast to dinner.
